metadata.description: VANC Is a Legendary Collection of 10,000 Volt Ape NFTs Which Are Direct Descendants of Volt Inu (The Electric Shock), a Very Popular and Quickly Rising Crypto. Volt Apes Hang Out In The Ethereum Blockchain Since That's Where They Like To Be. Your Ape Will Give You Access to Our Collaborative Play to Earn Game, To The Club, The Volt Inu Community, And Any Future Perks.
